wiki.content:
Third Single off the Forth Album, Billy Gibbons (ZZ TOP) features with lead Guitar and backup Vocals, Also seen in the Video Clip.
 
 This bit Stolen from WIKI
 "The song involves an exchange of vocal lines between the falsetto of Homme and the twin baritones of Gibbons and Mark Lanegan. Gibbons does not regularly tour with the band, so the other vocal was performed by Lanegan, until he stopped touring with the band. Currently, Josh Homme sings alone with backing vocals from the rest of the band, who lack either of the studio musicians' deep growls. In the previous line-up, Homme played bass and Alain Johannes played a quite different version of Gibbons' solo. This song was also featured in and on the soundtrack of 'Saw II."
